verbose_text: The PARP inhibitor PJ34 did not exert any cytotoxic effect in the used concentrations in our H9c2 cells and significantly protected these cells against H 2 O 2 induced injury in both concentrations (untreated + H 2 O 2, 35.14 +/-1.01%; 10 muM PJ34 + H 2 O 2, 15.65 +/-0.95%; 100 muM PJ34 + H 2 O 2, 15.69 +/-0.54%) (XREF_FIG).
evidence: PJ34 did not exert any cytotoxic effect in the used concentrations in our H9c2 cells and significantly protected these cells against H 2 O 2  induced injury
